abstract: |
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Multi-Agent System Development:</strong> Developed a multi-agent system with the PocketFlow framework, integrating RAG and message queues for XR software testing automation.</li>
    <li><strong>Inter-Agent Collaboration:</strong> Designed and implemented inter-agent collaboration workflows for efficient task coordination.</li>
    <li><strong>Unity Package Development:</strong> Created a configurable Unity package for automated multi-view data capture and camera parameter extraction in avatar-centered scenes.</li>
  </ul>



  


